Jesus. When I saw her, I was greatly astonished. 7 But the angel said to me, “Why
are you astonished? I will explain to you the meaning of the woman and of the beast
that is carrying her, the beast that has the seven heads and the ten horns. 8 The beast
you saw existed, does not exist now, but is about to come up from the bottomless pit.
