but it is one of those seven kings, and it is going to destruction. 12 The ten horns that
you saw are ten kings who have not yet received a kingdom, but they will receive
authority as kings for one hour together with the beast. 13 These are of one mind,
and they give over their power and authority to the beast. 14 They will wage war
against the Lamb. But the Lamb will conquer them because he is Lord of lords and
King of kings—and with him are the called ones, the chosen ones, and the faithful
